{"tid":2233121,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鐵騎士掛「光時」旗將轉高院審  國安法首案未定設陪審團","createTime":"2020-10-07T01:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T14:45:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"120a3ad68d73431f4c4c6095b9316d3c79a94af3","tid":2233121,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:41:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/G54DT4KU5VEJBO5NV7AJRFVAEM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2FG54DT4KU5VEJBO5NV7AJRFVAEM%2F&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmQjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=cc5eedbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201007%2FG54DT4KU5VEJBO5NV7AJRFVAEM%2F&h=e8206af9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201007/G54DT4KU5VEJBO5NV7AJRFVAEM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n鐵騎士掛「光時」旗將轉高院審 <br />\n國安法首案未定設陪審團<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】23歲侍應今年7.1涉嫌駕駛有「光復香港」旗幟的電單車撞傷三名警員，成為首名被控違反港版國安法的被告，案件昨再訊。控方修訂控罪地點範圍，由灣仔一帶擴闊至東隧至灣仔一帶道路，並在控罪中交代三名受傷警員的編號，又稱三人受重傷。律政司申請將案件轉介高等法院原訟庭審訊，至於會否設陪審團，代表在庭外稱暫未處理。<br />\n<br />\n男被告。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n恐怖活動罪則加入三名受傷警察身份，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/i6-2H8m7a2oE3wAy5YbdMBpTnkE=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5GSIFIX7LNBPXK4WJXXY2YVMSE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fi6-2H8m7a2oE3wAy5YbdMBpTnkE%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5GSIFIX7LNBPXK4WJXXY2YVMSE.jpg&h=0c83a9f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大批聲援市民昨傍晚在庭外亮起手機，送別運載被告的囚車。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被告還柙逾三月<br />\n<br />\n對於本案在高院審訊時會否設有陪審團，律政司一名檢控官庭外透露：「我哋未處理到呢度。」<br />\n<br />\n案發於今年7月1日，有市民響應號召上街反對港版國安法。當日被告駕駛插上「光復香港 時代革命」旗幟的電單車，其間被指撞傷三名警員，提堂後分別向裁判法院及高等法院申請保釋，均被拒絕，一直還柙。高院今年8月亦拒絕被告的人身保護令申請。<br />\n<br />\n一般而言，謀殺、誤殺、強姦、嚴重販毒等在高院原訟庭審訊的刑事案件，會由一名法官連同七名或九名陪審員審理，陪審團負責就案情事實作出裁斷，判被告有罪或無罪，法官則處理法律議題及量刑。不過，港版國安法設有「毋須陪審團」的審案安排，直接賦權律政司作決定。第46條指，律政司司長可基於保護國家秘密、案件具有涉外因素，或保障陪審員及其家人的人身安全等理由，發出證書指示相關訴訟毋須設陪審團。<br />\n<br />\n倘若律政司司長指示相關聆訊不設陪審團，港版國安法訂明須由三名法官組成審判庭，法例中有關陪審團的職責會被理解為法官作為事實裁斷者取而代之。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：WKCC2217/20<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VmBz7Jin5CmKK7TZafl8BynRcE8=/886x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/62JPK4PUZFA2LMWE5DGZDA4ZYY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVmBz7Jin5CmKK7TZafl8BynRcE8%3D%2F886x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F62JPK4PUZFA2LMWE5DGZDA4ZYY.jpg&h=2a782031&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告唐英傑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BX-li18KL3AMLDDV8HwrscDL0ns=/1356x910/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IIFORM2G4NCMRLVBUQOMVMJ4ZE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBX-li18KL3AMLDDV8HwrscDL0ns%3D%2F1356x910%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIIFORM2G4NCMRLVBUQOMVMJ4ZE.jpg&h=8b9fa404&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被告唐英傑涉於7月1日駕駛插上「光時」旗幟的電單車，被控煽動他人分裂國家。"},{"pid":"4866dc72bf14e3e0675b4899f27214a6975c2071","tid":2233121,"uid":209773,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:42:31.000Z","msg":"法治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbdc0aebe729d9f3868a512fa581cfe63c8c6548","tid":2233121,"uid":44209,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T01:44:11.000Z","msg":"插枝旗就話分裂國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且明明係班狗突然衝出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6R8Lga1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thum